summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 5926 for the improvement of 32nd Avenue South, from Plum Street to approximately 320 feet north thereof; and certain parts of certain other streets and avenues; by constructing sewers and watermains and otherwise improving the same; under Ordinance No. 78346, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
